# Summary

Use on **product projects** after OKF bootstrap. Forge is the **lifecycle planning layer**; OKF is the **curated memory substrate**; OKF dispatch is **implementation delivery**. Option C per `.okf/decisions/0002-okf-forge-integration.md`.

# Prerequisites

1. OKF five-service setup complete (or minimum Forge-only OKF per `docs/okf-ways-of-working-brief.md` § Forge-only minimum).
2. Sibling Forge repos built; Cursor MCP launchers resolve (`scripts/*-mcp.sh`).
3. `scripts/okf-validate` passes before and after promotion.

# Layer selection

| Trigger | Use | Canonical truth after review |
|---------|-----|------------------------------|
| Planning lifecycle stage (concept, build, launch, operate, …) | Forge MCP for stage | OKF concept after integrator promotion |
| Code, tests, implementation | OKF dispatch (`scripts/okf-dispatch`) | `.okf/handoffs/` + dispatch result |
| Cross-tool session resume, lease, relay handoff | ForgeRelay MCP | `.okf/handoffs/` + `relay_session_id` |
| External cited research | Perplexity MODE A → ingest | `.okf/references/` |
| Primary runner blocked | Perplexity MODE B overflow | `.okf/handoffs/` + overflow metadata |
| Learning synthesis across stages | InsightForge | `.okf/improvements/` after promotion |

**Rule:** Choose layer by **trigger**, not tool name. See `docs/okf-dispatch-orchestration.md` § Trigger-keyed decision matrix.

# Standard flow (Option C)

```text
1. Read OKF     → .okf/index.md, .okf/project.md, relevant concepts
2. Invoke Forge → planning-stage MCP tools; signed packets stay in .okf/forge/<stage>/ (gitignored)
3. Promote      → integrator-reviewed outcomes → OKF Markdown with Forge lineage (C2)
4. Dispatch     → builder/tester/reviewer/integrator via okf-dispatch
5. Log          → .okf/log.md; handoff if pausing
```

Forge workspaces under `.okf/forge/` are **runtime state**, not OKF concepts until promoted.

# SDLC quick map

See `docs/okf-ways-of-working-brief.md` § SDLC mapping and `docs/okf-forge-integration-spec.md` §5.

| Stage | Forge | OKF promotion target |
|-------|-------|---------------------|
| Discovery | ConceptForge | `.okf/requirements/` drafts |
| Design | BuildForge | requirements, architecture, decisions |
| Launch readiness | LaunchForge | `.okf/releases/`, test evidence |
| Post-launch | Operate, Customer, Growth, Revenue | workflows, features, references, decisions |
| Learning | InsightForge | `.okf/improvements/` |
| Governance | GovernanceForge | `.okf/decisions/`, `.okf/risks/` |
| Sunset | SunsetForge | archived handoffs |

