# Secrets and PII

- Never commit signing keys, approval receipts, or PII from Forge workspaces.
- Keys live outside git — see `.okf/references/forge-signing-keys-operator-runbook.md`.
- Receipt crypto: `forge-verify-receipt` before `verification_status: accepted` on Forge-sourced Decisions (decision 0004).

